shadow of Sir Tim Bell, Baroness Thatcher's image-maker and chairman of PR
firm Lowe Bell, still looms. Hill was previously a Lowe Bell employee; he is
returning there as a consultant.
Hill's post is being taken by Howell James - one of Bell's closest friends.
And when he was at Capital Radio, James employed Bell's wife, Virginia.
Nice to see Major sticking by family values.
